# No Barrel Files

**Do not create barrel files in this repo.** No `index.ts` (or similar) that re-exports from sibling files, including main package `src/index.ts`.

- Use direct subpath imports: `@repo/api/auth/hash`, `@repo/ui/composed/auth`, `@repo/db/schema/users`, etc.
- Export directly from each file via package.json exports
